Experiment 4: Addition of Two Numbers

Aim
To develop an Android application to add two numbers using EditText and Button controls.

Algorithm
1.Start Android Studio and create a new project.
2.Open activity_main.xml layout file.
3.Add two EditText fields to enter numbers.
4.Add Addition and Reset buttons.
5.Add a TextView to display the result.
6.Open MainActivity.java.
7.Connect the UI components using findViewById().
8.Set OnClickListener for the Addition button.
9.Convert the entered values into numbers and calculate the sum.
10.Display the result in the TextView.
11.Reset button clears the fields and result.
12.Run the application and verify the output.
